title: Couple With Heart Person Man No Skin Tone Medium Dark Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Person and man holding hands with heart
description: Depicts a couple, one person identified as a person and the other as a man, with a heart between them symbolizing love and romance. This version has medium-dark skin tones for both individuals.
apple_vendor_description: Apple’s rendering of this couple emoji showcases two figures embracing, with the man positioned slightly behind the woman. Their forms are imbued with Apple's characteristic glossy 3D shading and realistic lighting, creating a warm and connected visual. The medium-dark skin tone adds a touch of diversity and representation, while the prominent, softly glowing heart between them clearly symbolizes love, partnership, and a strong romantic bond on Apple devices.
